==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Montgolfier
<hw>Mont`gol"fier</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A balloon
which ascends by the buoyancy of air heated by a fire; a fire balloon;
-- so called from two brothers, Stephen and <person>Joseph
<etsep>Montgolfier</etsep></person>, of France, who first constructed
and sent up a fire balloon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Month</ent>⟦br⟧
